                       "skill":  "雄幕",
                       "key":  "dcxiongmu",
                       "index":  2,
                       "text":  "子衿乘风，欲访东翁，仿青梅煮酒，论天下英雄。",
                       "source":  "https://web.sanguosha.com/10/pc/res/assets/runtime/voice/skin/wuluxun02/WuLuXun_XiongMu_02.mp3",
                       "file":  "dcxiongmu2.mp3"
                   },
                   {
                       "skill":  "雄幕",
                       "key":  "dcxiongmu",
                       "index":  1,
                       "text":  "天下扰扰，英雄欲定乾坤，非一人之力可成。",
                       "source":  "https://web.sanguosha.com/10/pc/res/assets/runtime/voice/skin/wuluxun02/WuLuXun_XiongMu_01.mp3",
                       "file":  "dcxiongmu1.mp3"
                   },
                   {
                       "skill":  "彰才",
                       "key":  "dczhangcai",
                       "index":  1,
                       "text":  "何日试青锋？匣中长剑夜夜鸣。",
                       "source":  "https://web.sanguosha.com/10/pc/res/assets/runtime/voice/skin/wuluxun02/WuLuXun_ZhangCai_01.mp3",
                       "file":  "dczhangcai1.mp3"
                   },
                   {
                       "skill":  "彰才",
                       "key":  "dczhangcai",
                       "index":  2,
                       "text":  "江东山河甫定，正乃用武之时。",
                       "source":  "https://web.sanguosha.com/10/pc/res/assets/runtime/voice/skin/wuluxun02/WuLuXun_ZhangCai_02.mp3",
                       "file":  "dczhangcai2.mp3"
                   },
                   {
                       "skill":  "儒贤",
                       "key":  "dcruxian",
                       "index":  1,
                       "text":  "辅君以礼，匡国以行，泽民以仁，此为大道。",
                       "source":  "https://web.sanguosha.com/10/pc/res/assets/runtime/voice/skin/wuluxun02/WuLuXun_RuXian_01.mp3",
                       "file":  "dcruxian1.mp3"
                   },
                   {
                       "skill":  "儒贤",
                       "key":  "dcruxian",
                       "index":  2,
                       "text":  "万卷书，千里路，文如引帆之风，可至梦日之处。",
                       "source":  "https://web.sanguosha.com/10/pc/res/assets/runtime/voice/skin/wuluxun02/WuLuXun_RuXian_02.mp3",
                       "file":  "dcruxian2.mp3"
                   },
                   {
                       "skill":  "阵亡",
                       "key":  "die",
                       "index":  1,
                       "text":  "清翠白鹿隐，寻踪不知归。",
